tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: The patient shows a markedly low HbA1c, which may suggest recent hypoglycemia or conditions affecting red cell turnover. All other parameters are within normal limits except for a mildly decreased total CO₂, which could indicate mild metabolic acidosis or compensation for respiratory alkalosis. Clinical correlation is recommended.
